# ── Open-core boundary (ADR-0014) ────────────────────────────
# Pro / closed-source code MUST NOT live in this public repo.
# The Pro app + CleanerLicense live in the private `cleaner-pro` repo.
# These entries are defense-in-depth: if a Pro tree is ever checked out
# here by mistake, git will not stage it. (See ADR-0014 pre-push guard.)
pro/
/CleanerLicense/
**/CleanerLicense/
*.license
license/token.jws

# ── Local tool state (never commit user runtime data) ────────
.cleaner/

# Local agent guidance (not tracked in git)
CLAUDE.md
